Package ch.alexandrahauri.kiosk.controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArticleSelection
    Data Container for Article Selection, this just contains the Informations which are shown on the UI.
    ArticleSelectionController
    Controller for Article Selection, shows all the Articles which the kiosk has.
    CustomerInformationController
    Controller of Customer Information, asks for name and age input of the user
    KioskCreationController
    Controller of Kiosk Creation, asks for kioks Informations
    Overview  
    OverviewController
    Controller for Overview (Kiosk Manager), shows all the Kiosks.
    UIDataContainer
    Data Container in the Business View, UIDataContainer calls the Kioskmanager in the Business package UIDataContainer is a singleton
